## Early game

Entrati Lanthorn drops on the **Zariman** from **Halako Perimeter**
(Extermination), and also shows up as a **bounty reward** on both the
Zariman and Deimos's **Cambion Drift**. Running Halako Perimeter
Extermination gives you direct enemy-drop access, while rotating through a
few Entrati or Zariman bounty stages tends to net a Lanthorn or two per
bounty chain.

Bounty rewards come from a fixed reward table roll at bounty completion, so
**Resource Drop Boosters don't affect bounty-sourced Lanthorns** — they only
help if you're picking them up as in-mission drops on Halako Perimeter.

## Mid & late game

Once you're deep into Entrati and Holdfast crafting, alternate between
**Halako Perimeter Extermination** runs (for the boosted in-mission drop) and
stacking **Cambion Drift / Zariman bounties** back-to-back for their
Lanthorn reward slots. Since bounty rewards aren't booster-affected, the
efficient late-game loop is to save your Resource Drop Booster for
Extermination sessions and just grind bounty chains raw for the reward-table
copies.

